ng%20accepted.%20Equally%20hurting%20them%20is%20their%20corruption%20track%20record.%20People%20don't%20want%20such%20leadership%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20BJP%20is%20widely%20expected%20to%20win%20more%20than%20the%20required%20272%20seats%20needed%20for%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20elections%20for%20543%20seats%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20predicts%20the%20BJP%20will%20win%20370%20seats%20and%20its%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20more%20than%20400%2C%20aiming%20for%20a%20four-decade%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20India%20are%20witnessing%20what%20a%20determined%2C%20focused%20and%20result-oriented%20government%20can%20do.%20And%2C%20they%20want%20more%20of%20it.%20That%20is%20why%20from%20every%20corner%20of%20India%2C%20cutting%20across%20all%20sections%20of%20society%2C%20the%20people%20are%20saying%20in%20one%20voice-%20Ab%20Ki%20Baar%2C%20400%20Paar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConfident%20of%20his%20victory%20in%20the%20elections%2C%20PM%20Modi%20asserted%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20our%20third%20term%2C%20there's%20much%20work%20to%20be%20done.%20The%20last%20decade%20was%20about%20filling%20gaps%20created%20by%20those%20who%20ruled%20for%20seventy%20years.%20It%20was%20also%20about%20instilling%20a%20spirit%20of%20self-confidence%20that%20yes%2C%20India%20can%20become%20prosperous%20and%20self-reliant.%20We%20will%20build%20on%20this%20spirit%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20clearly%20see%20that%20the%20coming%20five%20years%20will%20be%20about%20our%20collective%20resolve%20of%20establishing%20the%20roadmap%20that%20will%20guide%20our%20trajectory%20as%20a%20nation%20for%20the%20next%20thousand%20years%20and%20make%20India%20the%20embodiment%20of%20prosperity%2C%20all-round%20growth%20and%20global%20leadership%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2096%20crore%20voters%20are%20eligible%20to%20exercise%20their%20franchise%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20said%2C%20of%20which%2049.72%20crore%20were%20male%20voters%20and%2047.1%20crore%20were%20female%20voters.%20There%20are%201.82%20crore%20first-time%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20polling%20was%20held%20in%20seven%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710590820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fbsgmdn48_pm-modi-pti_625x300_18_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-from-april-19-prime-minister-narendra-modi-says-bjp-nda-fully-prepared-5250783%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%2C%20the%20BJP-NDA%2C%20are%20fully%20prepared%2C%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20announced%20the%20schedule%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-from-april-19-prime-minister-narendra-modi-says-bjp-nda-fully-prepared-5250783%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-from-april-19-prime-minister-narendra-modi-says-bjp-nda-fully-prepared-5250783%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-from-april-19-prime-minister-narendra-modi-says-bjp-nda-fully-prepared-5250783%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha%20elections%202024%20Phase%202%3A%20Voting%20on%20April%2026%2C%20details%20here%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710590607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-05%2F13%2Ffull%2F1683939331-9356.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-p