hope%20to%20achieve%20is%20because%20of%20the%20munificence%20and%20blessing%20of%20their%20Supreme%20Leader%20%E2%80%93%20his%20face%20prominently%20displayed%20on%20top%20ensures%20that%20we%20get%20the%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20typical%20day%20%E2%80%93%20on%20March%2013%2C%20the%20Bombay%20edition%20of%20the%3Cem%3E%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20a%20full%20page%20ad%20by%20the%20Tata%20group%20welcoming%20Modi%20to%20lay%20the%20%E2%80%98virtual%20stone%20laying%E2%80%99%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Semiconductor%20Fab%20in%20Dholera%2C%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurn%20the%20pages%20and%20we%20are%20informed%20that%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government%20is%20delivering%20on%20%E2%80%98Modi%20ki%20Guarantee%E2%80%99%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98Visit%20to%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20his%20photo%20looms%20over%20the%20ad%20which%20tells%20us%20of%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98vision%E2%80%99%20for%20development%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20on%20two%20full%20pages%20by%20the%20UP%20government%20%E2%80%93%20again%20with%20Modi%20standing%20next%20too%20(but%20taller%20than)%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20hailing%20the%20%E2%80%98magnificent%E2%80%99%C2%A0%20infrastructure%20development%20and%20%E2%80%98cultural%2C%20spiritual%20and%20religious%20renaissance%E2%80%99.%20If%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20what%20this%20means%2C%20the%20ad%20spells%20it%20out%20in%20great%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20comes%20another%20Modi%20guarantee%20of%20World%20Class%20Dedicated%20Freight%20Corridors%20%E2%80%93%20its%20an%20ad%20by%20Indian%20Railways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiply%20this%20by%20the%20hundreds%20of%20newspapers%20in%20the%20country%20and%20also%20television%20channels%2C%20and%20one%20can%20imagine%20the%20sheer%20expense%20involved.%20The%20ads%20are%20paid%20for%20not%20by%20the%20BJP%20but%20by%20the%20respective%20governments%20and%20private%20sector%20companies%20and%20they%20generate%20revenue%20for%20the%20publications.%20One%20can%20understand%20why%20newspapers%20are%20reluctant%20to%20ask%20tough%20questions%20of%20the%20respective%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wall%20to%20wall%20coverage%20of%20Modi%20imagery%20and%20propaganda%20is%20not%20unusual%20%E2%80%93%20all%20these%20years%20(i.e.%20from%202014%20onwards)%2C%20his%20photos%20could%20be%20seen%20on%20hoardings%2C%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusiness.outlookindia.com%2Fnews%2Fgovt-s-new-design-for-fertilizer-bags-carries-pm-modi-s-appeal-to-farmers-to-reduce-use-of-chemical-crop-nutrients-news-311992%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520new%2520design%2520contains%2520an%2Cbalanced%2520use%2520of%2520chemical%2520fertilisers.%2522%5C%22%3Efertiliser%20bags%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20even%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-58944475%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20vaccination%20certificates%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Books%20on%20him%20and%20even%20by%20him%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FExam_Warriors%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EExam%20Warriors%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20published%20in%2013%20languages%2C%20have%20been%20released.%20He%20has%20published%20a%20book%20of%20poems%20in%20Gujarati%20which%20have%20been%20translated%20into%20Sanskrit.%20All%20this%20has%20fed%20into%20his%20cult%2C%20and%20created%20a%20larger%20than%20life%20image%20of%20a%20man%20who%20not%20only%20sold%20tea%20and%20brought%20a%20baby%20crocodile%20with%20him%2C%20to%20someone%20who%20is%20thoughtful%20and%20wise%20to%20one%20who%20hobnobs%20with%20world%20leaders%20as%20an%20equal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20different%20this%20time%20round%20is%20the%20concentrated%20focus%20on%20the%20performance%20and%20promises%20of%20the%20Modi%20sarkar%2C%20without%20any%20reference%20to%20the%20disasters%20of%20these%20past%2010%20years%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Faakar-patel-reserve-bank-of-india-demonetisation%5C%22%3Edemonetisation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fqz.com%2Fhow-china-has-been-nibbling-away-at-indian-territory-1850297445%5C%22%3Etakeover%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Indian%20land%20by%20China.%20That%20is%20what%20parties%20do%20when%20elections%20are%20coming%2C%20but%20not%20in%20such%20a%20concentrated%20manner%20and%20not%20by%20using%20public%20funds.%20Fully%20aware%20that%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20may%20not%20be%20as%20rosy%20as%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20ministers%20talk%20about%2C%20the%20campaign%20is%20full%20of%20grand%20claims%20and%20assurances.%20A%20word%20to%20the%20copy%20writer%20though%20%E2%80%93%20A%20headline%20like%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Vanchiton%20ki%20Varivata%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20wasted%20in%20an%20English%20newspaper%2C%20and%20perhaps%20even%20in%20a%20Hindi%20one%2C%20but%20that%20is%20how%20the%20Sangh%20thinks%20and%20speaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20is%20taking%20no%20chances%20%E2%80%93%20it%20has%20broken%20up%20with%20old%20allies%20and%20aligned%20with%20those%20it%20called%20corrupt%20%E2%80%93%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20in%20Maharashtra.%20It%20has%20worked%20to%20break%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Bihar%2C%20for%20instance.%20It%20has%20let%20loose%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fed-cbi-devious-track-record%5C%22%3Eenforcement%20agencies%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20fully%20aware%20that%20it%20now%20needs%20seats%20from%20beyond%20the%20states%20that%20usually%20support%20it%20%E2%80%93%20UP%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20the%20Hindi-speaking%20belt%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20doing%20everything%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20remains%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20voters%E2%80%99%20mind%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20Modi%20is%20the%20biggest%20draw%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20natural%20that%20he%20is%20projected%20the%20most%20by%20way%20of%20these%20daily%20ads%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20our%20tax%20money%20has%20to%20pay%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20sarkar%20is%20a%20conceited%20way%20of%20suggesting%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%98his%E2%80%99%20government%20%E2%80%93%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20collective%20just%20does%20not%20exist%20in%20the%20BJP%20as%20of%20today%2C%20once%20proud%20of%20being%20a%20collegial%20party%2C%20where%20no%20one%20person%20was%20above%20the%20other.%20Now%20it%20is%20Modi%2C%20Modi%20and%20more%20Modi%2C%20but%20only%20up%20to%20a%20point%20%E2%80%93%20all%20successes%20are%20his%2C%20all%20failures%20are%20because%20of%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20at%20all%20the%20party%20and%20its%20allies%20do%20not%20get%20the%20400%20seats%2C%20370%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20that%20it%20is%20aiming%20for%20%E2%80%93%20apparently%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-mp-says-partys-400-seat-goal-for-2024-is-so-it-can-change-constitution%5C%22%3Echange%20the%20constitution%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20an%20MP%20from%20Karnataka%20has%20helpfully%20informed%20us%20%E2%80%93%20who%20will%20get%20the%20blame%3F%20This%20is%20not%20just%20pre-election%20rhetoric%2C%20Modi%20genuinely%20wants%20to%20break%20previous%20records.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20ambitious%20target%20to%20reach%3B%20in%20fact%20303%2C%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20it%20won%20the%20last%20time%2C%20also%20looks%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20promises%20%E2%80%93%20removing%20Article%20370%2C%20a%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20Rules%20%E2%80%93%20have%20all%20been%20fulfilled.%20But%20he%20knows%20that%20ultimately%20the%20voters%20want%20to%20know%20how%20the%20government%20will%20change%20their%20life%20for%20the%20better%20%E2%80%93%20hence%20the%20ads%20are%20not%20about%20those%20%E2%80%98achievements%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20about%20jobs%2C%20education%2C%20houses.%20The%20macro%20figures%20about%20India%E2