20to%20run%20from%20April%2019%20to%20June%201%20-%20in%20which%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20BJP%20will%20bid%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%2C%20and%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20opposition%20bloc%20will%20try%20and%20stop%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20speculation%20the%20poll%20panel%20might%20also%20confirm%20dates%20for%20an%20election%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20which%20is%20under%20President's%20Rule%20and%20has%20not%20held%20an%20Assembly%20election%20for%20nearly%20six%20years%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20materialise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20will%20hold%20its%20parliamentary%20election%20in%20five%20phases%20-%20April%2019%2C%20April%2026%2C%20May%207%2C%20May%2013%2C%20May%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20directed%20the%20conduct%20of%20an%20Assembly%20election%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20by%20September%2030%2C%202024%2C%20as%20the%20first%20step%20in%20restoration%20of%20statehood.%20The%20order%20was%20part%20of%20the%20verdict%20on%20pleas%20challenging%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710589320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-10%2Ft6j70hbg_jammu-kashmir-elections_625x300_08_October_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-dates-j-k-voting-no-simultaneous-lok-sabha-assembly-polls-for-j-k-5250220%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20not%20hold%20simultaneous%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20said%20Saturday%2C%20as%20he%20announced%20dates%20for%20the%20general%20election%20and%20four%20state%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-dates-j-k-voting-no-simultaneous-lok-sabha-assembly-polls-for-j-k-5250220%22%2C%2