d%20member%20of%20the%20team%20and%20I%20thoroughly%20enjoyed%20working%20with%20him.%20But%2C%20in%20every%20institution%2C%20everyone%20must%20be%20given%20personal%20space%2C%20and%20that%20should%20not%20be%20touched.%20He%20had%20his%20reasons%2C%20and%20you%20should%20ask%20him%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20let%20me%20be%20clear...%20we%20have%20a%20very%20sound%20tradition%20of%20not%20stifling%20dissent%20within%20the%20four%20walls%20of%20the%20ECI.%20This%20(the%20planning%20and%20conduct%20of%20elections)%20is%20a%20very%20complicated%20exercise...%20and%20three%20minds%20are%20always%20better%20than%20one...%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20when%20Mr%20Goel%20said%20he%20was%20stepping%20down%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20he%20too%20had%20cited%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20reasons%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20said%20the%20government%20had%20persuaded%20to%20reconsider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-election-commissioner-arun-goel-resigned-due-to-personal-reasons-sources-5210010%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhy%20Election%20Commissioner%20Arun%20Goel%20Resigned%20Weeks%20Before%202024%20Polls%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20dismissed%20speculation%20ill%20health%20had%20forced%20to%20resign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goel%20was%20appointed%20in%20November%202022%3B%20this%20was%20a%20day%20after%20he%20quit%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20then%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20is%20the%20tearing%20hurry%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20to%20have%20served%20till%202027%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20Mr%20Goel%20was%20in%20line%20to%20replace%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20as%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20after%20the%20latter%20retires%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Arun%20Goel's%20resignation%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20was%20the%20only%20person%20on%20the%20three-member%20poll%20panel%20till%20two%20new%20officers%20were%20inducted%20-%20ex-civil%20servants%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%20and%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu.%20They%20replaced%20Mr%20Goel%20and%20Anup%20Pandey%2C%20whose%20term%20expired%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-to-begin-from-april-19-will-be-held-in-7-phases-results-on-june-4-5250075%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELok%20Sabha%20Elections%20From%20April%2019%20In%207%20Phases%2C%20Results%20On%20June%204%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20this%20afternoon%20announced%20the%20schedule%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20Assembly%20election%20and%20for%20state%20polls%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Odisha%2C%20and%20Sikkim%2C%20as%20well%20as%20bypolls%20to%2026%20Assembly%20constituencies%20across%2013%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolling%20for%20all%20begins%20on%20April%2019%2C%20with%20the%20general%20election%20spread%20over%20seven%20phases.%20Results%20for%20all%20elections%20will%20be%20declared%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710588600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fnlq69gi8_chief-election-commissioner-rajiv-kumar_625x300_16_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpersonal-reasons-poll-panel-chief-on-arun-goels-shock-resignation-5250560%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20steered%20clear%20of%20a%20question%20on%20last%20week's%20shock%20resignation%20of%20Arun%20Goel%20as%20an%20Election%20Commissioner%20-%20days%20before%20the%20poll%20panel%20was%20to%20announce%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20dates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpersonal-reasons-poll-panel-chief-on-arun-goels-shock-resignation-5250560%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpersonal-reasons-poll-panel-chief-on-arun-goels-shock-resignation-5250560%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpersonal-reasons-poll-panel-chief-on-arun-goels-shock-resignation-5250560%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Eve%20of%20Election%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20Enhances%20Quota%20of%20Politically%20Influential%20Paharis%2C%20Expands%20OBC%20List%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F16163329%2FUntitled-design-49.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Less%20than%2024%20hours%20before%20the%20imposition%20of%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20(MCC)%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20administration%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20on%20Friday%20evening%20announced%20amendments%20to%20the%20Union%20territory%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20rules%20to%20enhance%20the%20quota%20of%20politically%20influential%20Pahari%20community%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20addition%20of%2015%20more%20communities%20in%20the%20latter%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20move%20shows%20that%20the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20derive%20electoral%20mileage%20from%20it%20in%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReservation%20for%20Paharis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UT%E2%80%99s%20administrative%20council%20headed%20by%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20cleared%20a%20proposal%20to%20grant%2010%25%20reservation%20to%20Pahari%20ethnic%20tribe%2C%20Paddari%20tribe%2C%20Kolis%20and%20Gadda%20Brahmin%20communities.%20The%20quota%20of%20these%20communities%20was%20announced%20two%20months%20after%20the%20parliament%20passed%20a%20bill%20to%20declare%20them%20as%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20just%20a%20day%20before%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20announced%20the%20schedule%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20cleared%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20respectively%20on%20February%206%20and%209%2C%20the%20President%20of%20India%20gave%20assent%20to%20the%20bill%20on%20February%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20four%20communities%20notified%20as%20STs%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20the%20politically%20significant%20Pahari%20community%20was%20entitled%20to%204%25%20reservation%20from%202019%20onwards%20after%20the%20then%20Governor%20Satya%20Pal%20Malik%20gave%20assent%20to%20a%20bill%20granting%20them%20reservation%20in%20jobs%20and%20admissions%20in%20government-run%20professional%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grant%20of%20ST%20status%20to%20Paharis%20evoked%20widespread%20resentment%20from%20Gujjar-Bakerwal%20communities%2C%20who%20alleged%20that%20the%20move%20was%20aimed%20at%20diluting%20their%20tribal%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20pacify%20the%20Gujjar-Bakerwal%20communities%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20LG-led%20administration%20have%20repeatedly%20maintained%20from%2020222%20that%20their%20quota%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20grant%20of%20reservation%20to%20Paharis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20balancing%20act%20between%20the%20two%20communities%2C%20both%20Paharis%20and%20three%20other%20communities%20declared%20as%20STs%20this%20year%20and%20STs%20notified%20earlier%20would%20now%20get%2010%25%20reservation%20each%2C%20taking%20reservation%20of%20ST%20category%20to%2020%25%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grant%20of%20ST%20status%20to%20Paharis%20and%20enhancement%20of%20their%20quota%20is%20part%20of%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20plan%20to%20woo%20the%20Pahari%20community%2C%20which%20is%20in%20majority%20in%20seven%20out%20of%20eight%20segments%20of%20the%20Pir%20Panchal%20region%2C%20comprising%20Muslim-majority%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch%20districts.%20Of%20these%20seven%20segments%2C%20six%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20is%20likely%20to%20benefit%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20Lok%20Sabha%20segment%2C%20which%20is%20the%20first-ever%20electoral%20unit%20that%20transcends%20the%20geographical%20boundaries%20of%20Kashmir%20and%20Jammu%20region.%20This%20seat%20comprising%2018%20assembly%20segments%20%E2%80%93%20seven%20of%20Jammu%20and%2011%20of%20Kashmir%20%E2%80%93%20is%20partly%20riddled%20with%20caste%20faultlines%20and%20partly%20witnessed%20low%20turnout%20in%20elections%20after%201987%20polls%20which%20were%20rigged%20and%20believed%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20main%20causes%20behind%20armed%20militancy%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20carving%20out%20of%20the%20seat%20by%20the%20delimitation%20commission%20was%20dubbed%20as%20a%20brazen%20instance%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgerrymandering%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Celectoral%20manipulation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20groups%20and%20enhancement%20of%20OBC%20quota%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administrative%20council%20has%20also%20added%2015%20more%20communities%20to%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20besides%20enhancing%20their%20quota%20to%208%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20classes%20being%20added%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20OBC%20list%20include%20Waghey%20(Chopan)%2C%20Ghirath%2FBhati%2FChang%20community%2C%20Jat%20community%2C%20Saini%20community%2C%20Markabans%2FPonywalas%2C%20Sochi%20community%2C%20Christian%20Biradari%20(converted%20from%20Hindu%20Valmiki)%2C%20Sunar%2FSwarankar%20Teeli%20(Hindu%20Teeli%20along%20with%20already%20existing%20Muslim%20Teli)%2C%20Perna%2FKouro(Kaurav)%2C%20Bojru%2FDecount%2FDubdabay%20Brahmin%2C%20Gorkans%2C%20Gorkhas%2C%20West%20Pakistani%20refugees%20(excluding%20SCs)%20and%20Acharyas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20recognising%20new%20social%20groups%2C%20the%20government%20also%20enhanced%20the%20quota%20of%20OBCs%20to%208%25%20from%204%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20amendment%20in%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Reservation%20Act%20in%20December%202023%2C%20the%20OBCs%20were%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9Cweak%20and%20underprivileged%20classes%20(social%20castes)%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20UT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20declaration%20of%20these%20communities%20as%20OBCs%20and%20enhancement%20of%20their%20quota%20would%20strengthen%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20grip%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Udhampur%20seats%2C%20which%20the%20party%20had%20won%20consecutively%20in%20the%202014%20and%202019%20LS%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETiming%20shows%20electoral%20motives%20behind%20the%20move%3A%20Opposition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20four-time%20MLA%20and%20senior%20CPI%20(M)%20leader%20MY%20Tarigami%20attributed%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20motives%20behind%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20for%20the%20election%20purposes%20and%20that%20is%20why%20the%20announcement%20has%20been%20made%20a%20day%20before%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20spokesperson%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20unit%20of%20Congress%2C%20Ravinder%20Sharma%20said%20the%20timing%20of%20these%20amendments%20shows%20that%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20wants%20to%20derive%20electoral%20mileage%20from%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20should%20have%20announced%20the%20quota%20for%20Paharis%20and%20other%20communities%20immediately%20after%20the%20President%20of%20India%20gave%20assent%20to%20the%20bill%20granting%20ST%20status%20to%20them%2C%20but%20they%20delayed%20it%20due%20to%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710588558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F16163329%2FUntitled-design-49