0final%20advisory.%20So%20this%20is%20how%20we%20have%20set%20our%20grounds.%20We%20are%20putting%20political%20parties%20on%20notice.%20We%20have%20asked%20political%20parties%20to%20give%20copies%20of%20our%20guidelines%20to%20each%20star%20campaigner%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710584820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1ndsal5_election-commissioner-650-_650x400_16_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-cross-red-line-during-campaign-election-commission-to-political-parties-5250011%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stressing%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20adhering%20to%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20has%20warned%20parties%20not%20to%20cross%20the%20red%20line%20while%20campaigning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-cross-red-line-during-campaign-election-commission-to-political-parties-5250011%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-cross-red-line-during-campaign-election-commission-to-political-parties-5250011%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-cross-red-line-during-campaign-election-commission-to-political-parties-5250011%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Updates%3A%207-Phase%20Lok%20Sabha%20Election%20Dates%20Announced%2C%20No%20Simultaneous%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20said%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20is%20working%20towards%20combating%20the%C2%A04Ms%20(muscle%2C%20money%2C%20misinformation%2C%20and%20MCC%20violations)%20that%20hinder%20the%20path%20to%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Election%20Commission%20is%20holding%20a%20press%20conference%20to%20announce%20the%20schedule%20of%20the%20