0SKM%E2%80%99s%20rally%20was%20held%20near%20where%20the%20scenes%20of%20January%2026%2C%202021%20took%20place%2C%20when%20farmers%20demonstrated%20in%20large%20numbers%20outside%20the%20Red%20Fort%2C%20and%20recalled%20the%20powerful%20movement%20of%202020-2021%20which%20forced%20the%20government%20to%20repeal%20the%20three%20farm%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20photographs%20of%20masses%20of%20people%2C%20these%20photographs%20are%20portraits%20of%20individuals%20who%20attended%20the%20SKM%E2%80%99s%20rally%20with%20a%20view%20to%20putting%20faces%20to%20the%20activists%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F16135235%2F1-288A3648.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F16135235%2F1-288A3648.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F16135235%2F1-288A3648-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F16135235%2F1-288A3648-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701942%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20protestor%20at%20Kisan%20Mahapanchayat%20at%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20in%20Delhi%20on%20March%2014.%20Photo%3A%20Zaen%20Alkazi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F16135840%2F2-288A3848.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-cont