%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffirms-linked-to-kolkata-industrialist-mahendra-jalan-spent-rs-617-crore-on-electoral-bonds%5C%22%3EFirms%20Linked%20to%20Kolkata%20Industrialist%20Mahendra%20Jalan%20Spent%20Rs%20617%20Crore%20on%20Electoral%20Bonds%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Dhulian%2C%20Murshidabad%2C%20women%20beedi%20workers%20are%20frequent%20buyers%2C%20often%20using%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20daily%20wages.%20One%20such%20woman%2C%20hopeful%20of%20changing%20her%20life%2C%20justifies%20spending%20this%20money.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20my%20%3Cem%3Eharam%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bunlawful%5D%20money.%20Every%20day%2C%20I%20spend%20thirty%20rupees%20from%20my%20wage%20to%20buy%20tickets.%20If%20I%20am%20lucky%2C%20I%20will%20get%20it.%20If%20not%2C%20I%20know%20I%20am%20not%20lucky.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamir%20Mondal%2C%20a%20lottery%20ticket%20seller%20confirms%20that%20his%20customers%20are%20primarily%20those%20struggling%20financially%2C%20along%20with%20some%20unemployed%20businessmen.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20quick%20route%20to%20get%20rich.%20Mostly%20poor%20and%20unemployed%20people%20buy%20tickets.%20Very%20seldom%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20rich%20buying%20lottery%20tickets.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Bangla%20to%20English%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710579654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F16135843%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-16-at-1.57.50-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftrinamool-congress-links-emerge-in-future-gaming-lottery-winners-a-major-electoral-bond-contributor%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Across%20West%20Bengal%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sharp%20increase%20in%20suicide%20due%20to%20lottery%20addiction.%20While%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20top%20purchaser%20of%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20donating%20approximately%20Rs%201%2C368%20crore%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20is%20the%20second%20largest%20recipient%20of%20the%20bonds%20totalling%20Rs%201609%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftrinamool-congress-links-emerge-in-future-gaming-lottery-winners-a-major-electoral-bond-contributor%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lucknow%3A%20Women%20Who%20Had%20Protested%20Against%20CAA%20in%202020%20Put%20Under%20'House%20Arrest'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F14191540%2Fimage11-16.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELucknow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Women%20who%20led%20the%20protest%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20in%20Lucknow%20in%202020%20alleged%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Police%20put%20them%20under%20house%20arrest%20on%20March%2015%2C%20Friday.%20According%20to%20these%20protesters%2C%20the%20administration%20has%20been%20exerting%20pressure%20on%20them%20not%20to%20raise%20their%20voices%20against%20the%20new%20citizenship%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20daughters%20of%20the%20well-known%20Urdu%20poet%20Munawwar%20Rana%20also%20alleged%20that%20they%20had%20been%20under%20house%20arrest%20from%20the%20morning%20to%20the%20evening%20of%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20these%20women%20protesters%20residing%20in%20different%20localities%20of%20the%20state%20capital%20say%20that%20they%20adhere%20to%20their%20stand%20to%20oppose%20the%20CAA%2C%20which%20according%20to%20them%20is%20discriminating%20and%20against%20the%20constitution%20of%20India.%20Besides%20this%2C%20a%20heavy%20police%20force%20was%20deployed%20around%20the%20iconic%20Ghanta%20Ghar%2C%20Hussainabad%2C%20which%20was%20the%20epicentre%20of%20nearly%20two%20months-long%20anti-CAA%20protests%20in%20Lucknow%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20alleged%20that%20police%20knocked%20on%20their%20doors%20on%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20not%20allowing%20them%20to%20move%20anywhere%20from%20their%20houses.%20A%20woman%20protestor%20says%20that%20police%20came%20to%20her%20house%20for%20the%20first%20time%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20March%2011%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20notification%20of%20CAA%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEram%20Fatima%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20architects%20of%20the%202020%20protest%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20police%20visited%20her%20flat%20in%20Napier%20Road%20Colony%20every%20day%20since%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20CAA%20was%20announced.%20%E2%80%9CPolice%20have%20been%20deployed%20outside%20my%20apartment%2C%20and%20policemen%20are%20interrogating%20every%20guest%20visiting%20the%20apartment.%20This%20is%20humiliating%20for%20me%20and%20irritating%20for%20my%20neighbours%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Eram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%2C%20the%20police%20also%20sent%20notices%20to%20some%20other%20women%20protestors%20and%20summoned%20them%20to%20police%20stations.%20However%2C%20she%20did%20not%20disclose%20their%20names.%20A%20staunch%20opponent%20of%20the%20CAA%20Eram%20believes%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20imposed%20a%20new%20citizenship%20law%20to%20hide%20its%20failure%20on%20every%20front%20including%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%2C%20the%20agrarian%20crisis%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20visited%20the%20house%20of%20Uzma%20Parveen%2C%20well-known%20as%20Lucknow%20ki%20Jhansi%20ki%20Rani%2C%20on%20Friday%20morning%20around%2010%20am.%20Uzma%20says%20police%20allegedly%20put%20her%20under%20house%20arrest%20and%20crippled%20her%20movement%20until%20the%20evening.%20According%20to%20Uzma%2C%20her%20phone%20was%20switched%20off%2C%20so%20the%20police%20used%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20(60)%2C%20who%20is%20sick%20these%20days%2C%20contact%20number%20to%20communicate%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20sees%20this%20as%20intimidation%20for%20those%20who%20protested%20against%20the%20arrogance%20of%20the%20government%20in%20the%20past%20and%20launched%20anti-CAA%20protests.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20utterly%20shameful%20that%20the%20police%20are%20humiliating%20us%20during%20the%20holy%20month%20of%20Ramzaan%20while%20we%20are%20keeping%20fast%20and%20devoting%20most%20of%20our%20time%20to%20prayers%2C%20etc.%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daughters%20of%20the%20late%20Urdu%20poet%20Munawwar%20Rana%20also%20claim%20that%20the%20police%20put%20them%20under%20house%20arrest.%20Sumaiya%20Rana%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20strongly%20opposed%20her%20house%20last%20night%20and%20argued%20with%20the%20police%2C%20which%20disallowed%20her%20to%20move%20anywhere%20in%20the%20city%20for%20nearly%2024%20hours.%20Munawwar%E2%80%99s%20daughters%20were%20present%20at%20Ghanta%20Ghar%20from%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20anti-CAA%20protest%2C%20which%20began%20after%20being%20inspired%20by%20the%20Shaheen%20Bagh%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20police%20came%20to%20Sumaiya%E2%80%99s%20flat%2C%20Silver%20Apartment%2C%20in%20the%20Qaiserbag%20locality.%20Police%20knocked%20at%20her%20door%20several%20times%20earlier%20since%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20was%20lifted.%20Police%20also%20severed%20her%20notices%20many%20times%20and%20summoned%20her%20to%20the%20local%20police%20station%20in%20the%20past.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20put%20us%20under%20arrest%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20democratic%20voices.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20police%20used%20to%20sit%20in%20parking%20at%20my%20apartment%2C%20but%20this%20time%20cops%20entered%20my%20flat%2C%20sat%20inside%20my%20home%20and%20did%20not%20allow%20me%20to%20go%20meet%20my%20widow%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20who%20is%20residing%20in%20the%20other%20locality%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sumaiya%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20criticising%20the%20CAA%2C%20she%20said%20this%20law%20was%20neither%20acceptable%20earlier%20nor%20today%2C%20and%20democratic%20protests%20against%20it%20would%20be%20continued%20until%20the%20government%20would%20not%20roll%20back%20it.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20law%20based%20on%20religion%20is%20not%20acceptable%3B%20we%20are%20not%20fearful%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20abuse%20of%20power%3B%20we%20would%20raise%20our%20voice%20against%20the%20new%20citizenship%20law%20which%20discriminates%20people%20based%20on%20their%20religious%20identity%2C%20says%20an%20SP%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPolice%20in%20six-seven%20vehicles%20came%20to%20my%20home%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20sat%20in%20my%20drawing%20room%20for%20the%20whole%20day%2C%20not%20permitting%20me%20to%20go%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Uroosa%20Rana.%20She%20is%20also%20the%20daughter%20of%20Munawwar%20Rana.%20Urosa%20is%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20UP%20Mahila%20Congress%20(Central%20Zone).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnoyed%20by%20her%20alleged%20house%20arrest%2C%20Uroosa%20says%20UP%20police%20were%20behaving%20with%20protestors%20as%20criminals.%20%E2%80%9CWas%20the%20right%20to%20protest%20abolished%20by%20the%20government%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20questioned.%20If%20not%2C%20why%20is%20the%20government%20ruining%20our%20lives%20by%20sending%20police%20every%20day%20to%20our%20houses%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Uroosa%2C%20such%20actions%20show%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20fearful%20and%20perturbed%20since%20the%20notification%20of%20discriminatory%20laws.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20facing%20such%20humiliation%20for%20raising%20voices%20against%20the%20dictatorial%20attitudes%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20because%20of%20our%20Muslim%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UP%20police%20confirmed%20that%20the%20cops%20went%20to%20the%20places%20of%20some%20protestors%20but%20denied%20the%20house%20arrest%20of%20any%20of%20them.%20While%20talking%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20the%20Police%20(Central)%20Raveena%20Tyagi%20said%20police%20were%20deployed%20outside%20some%20protestors%E2%80%99%20houses%20to%20keep%20a%20vigil%20on%20them%20to%20maintain%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20DCP%20also%20added%20that%20no%20one%20was%20under%20house%20arrest%3B%20it%20was%20only%20a%20primitive%20step%20to%20avoid%20any%20untoward%20incident.%20Today%2C%20on%20the%20first%20Friday%20of%20the%20Islamic%20month%20Ramzaan%2C%20heavy%20police%20were%20deployed%20outside%20the%20mosques%20as%20police%20were%20anticipating%20the%20outbreak%20of%20protests%20against%20the%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Lucknow%2C%20police%20flags%20marched%20in%20Muslim%20localities%2C%20especially%20around%20mosques.%20Massive%20protests%20broke%20out%20in%20UP%20on%20December%2019%2C%202019%2C%20when%20some%20opposition%20parties%20and%20civil%20society%20gave%20a%20call%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20CAA.%20More%20than%2020%20protesters%20died%20in%20a%20state-wide%20protest%20allegedly%20caused%20by%20police%20bullets%2C%20which%20the%20police%20never%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20women%20also%20protested%20against%20it%20at%20Ghanta%20Ghar%20for%20nearly%20two%20months%20between%20January%202020%20and%20March%202020.%20The%20protest%20was%20withdrawn%20due%20to%20the%20nationwide%20lockdown%20due%20to%20the%20outbreak%20of%20COVID-19.%20Later%20on%2C%20police%20pitched%20camps%20on%20Ghanta%20Ghar%20premises%2C%20and%20no%20one%20was%20allowed%20to%20protest%20there.%20Today%2C%20police%20turned%20Ghanta%20Ghar%20into%20a%20fortress%2C%20and%20an%20additional%20police%20force%20was%20deployed%20at%20the%20protest%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710577798000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F14191540%2Fimage11-16.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22htt