tributions%20by%20companies%20came%20only%20after%20they%20were%20raided%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20minister%20suggests%20that%20bonds%20could%20have%20been%20bought%20before%20the%20raids.%20She%20may%20be%20jumping%20the%20gun%20as%20more%20revelations%20in%20this%20regard%20are%20in%20the%20offing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20ED%2C%20Income%20Tax%20department%20and%20CBI%2C%20in%20what%20appears%20like%20an%20institutionalised%20extortion%20racket%2C%20was%20revealed%20earlier%20in%20an%20investigation%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2024%2F02%2F21%2Fpart-2-30-firms-who-donated-rs-335-cr-to-bjp-were-also-stung-by-i-t-ed%5C%22%3Eshowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20over%20Rs%20300%20crore%20of%20electoral%20funding%20via%20the%20open%20trust%20route%20by%20some%20companies%20happened%20after%20investigations%20were%20launched%20against%20them%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20Income%20Tax%20department.%20This%20pattern%20is%20now%20also%20visible%20among%20the%20companies%20which%20have%20contributed%20huge%20sums%20via%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20anti-corruption%20plank%20was%20badly%20dented%20during%20the%20Karnataka%20elections%20itself%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fkarnataka-polls-resulty-congress-bjp-40-cut-in-contractor-suicide-note-became-key-point-in-opp-script-8607979%2F%5C%22%3Echarge%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%E2%80%9C40%25%20Sarkara%E2%80%9D%20had%20defined%20the%20character%20of%20the%20BJP%20rule.%20Large%20infrastructure%20projects%2C%20tom-tommed%20as%20a%20key%20driver%20of%20growth%20in%20the%20Modi%20era%2C%20seem%20to%20have%20opened%20floodgates%20of%20payouts%20so%20omnipresent%20in%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20saga.%20Guaranteed%20commissions%20seem%20to%20be%20the%20name%20of%20the%20game.%20It%20can%20easily%20appear%20in%20one%20of%20the%20ads%20of%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CModi%20ki%20Guarantee%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E(Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantee).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1065271%2Fmodi-used-electoral-bonds-to-run-worlds-largest-extortion-racket-says-rahul-gandhi%5C%22%3Ehas%20charged%3C%2Fa%3E%20Modi%20with%20running%20the%20biggest%20extortion%20racket%20in%20the%20name%20of%20electoral%20bonds.%20The%20opposition%20parties%20are%20likely%20to%20escalate%20this%20campaign%20against%20Modi%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%20as%20the%20election%20campaign%20hots%20up.%20True%2C%20opposition%20parties%2C%20too%2C%20have%20also%20got%20funds%20from%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20each%20receiving%20about%205%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20what%20BJP%20had%20got.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20includes%20the%20other%20official%20sources%20of%20funding%20such%20as%20the%20electoral%20trust%20route%20and%20the%20Rs%2020%2C000%20and%20above%20contributions%20which%20are%20recorded%2C%20the%20share%20of%20the%20opposition%20goes%20down%20even%20further%20as%20the%20BJP%20has%20received%2080%25%20to%2085%25%20of%20those%20monies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20evident%20the%20playing%20field%20is%20very%20skewed%20and%20the%20institutionalised%20misuse%20of%20agencies%20like%20ED%20and%20Income%20Tax%20department%20has%20largely%20contributed%20to%20this.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20become%20quite%20brazen%20about%20it.%20Sometime%20ago%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20boasted%20that%20his%20government%20had%20the%20unique%20distinction%20of%20having%20seized%20over%20Rs%201.12%20lakh%20crore%20worth%20of%20assets%20of%20companies%20and%20individuals%20during%20his%20tenure.%20The%20ED%20has%20been%20on%20steroids%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years%20and%20its%20conviction%20rate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fed-low-conviction-rate-caged-parrot-that-cant-get-anyone-to-sing%5C%22%3Eremains%20as%20low%20as%200.5%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20PMLA%20cases%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20moot%20question%20how%20many%20of%20these%20companies%20whom%20the%20ED%2C%20CBI%20or%20Income%20Tax%20department%20were%20pursuing%20bought%20electoral%20bonds.%20Many%20small%20companies%20may%20have%20acted%20as%20front%20companies%20like%20the%20one%20which%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20private%2C%20unlisted%20subsidiary%20of%20Reliance%20Retail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20came%2C%20there%20was%20a%20ceiling%20of%207.5%25%20of%20the%20previous%20three%20years%E2%80%99%20net%20profits%20beyond%20which%20companies%20could%20not%20donate.%20There%20was%20a%20reason%20for%20this%20ceiling.%20It%20limited%20the%20quid%20pro%20quo%20element%20to%20some%20extent%20and%20protected%20the%20shareholders%20interest%20too.%20And%20it%20was%20revealed%20by%20both%20the%20political%20party%20and%20the%20company%20in%20their%20respective%20books.%20There%20was%20far%20more%20transparency%20then.%20The%20Electoral%20Bond%20scheme%20just%20removed%20the%20ceiling%20on%20net%20profits%20and%20made%20the%20contributions%20anonymous.%20This%20was%20an%20invitation%20to%20corruption%20as%20the%20nature%20of%20companies%20that%20have%20bought%20electoral%20bonds%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20scheme%20is%20a%20can%20of%20worms%20is%20not%20in%20doubt%20anymore.%20A%20large%20group%20like%20Vedanta%20is%20shown%20as%20having%20contributed%20over%20Rs%20300%20crore%20between%202019%20and%202022%20while%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20CBI.%20Worse%2C%20during%20this%20period%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20also%20handpicks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fcons-products%2Felectronics%2Fvedanta-to-soon-have-a-tech-partner-for-semicon-ambitions-after-foxconn-break-up%2Farticleshow%2F102192765.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EVedanta%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fvedanta-to-invest-5bn-in-first-phase-for-semicon-fab-comfortable-in-debt-position-anil-agarwal-11690544737735.html%5C%22%3Eas%20a%20partner%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zeebiz.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews-identified-world-class-tech-partner-in-process-of-tying-with-them-anil-agarwal-on-vedantas-chip-plans-246537%5C%22%3Eof%20the%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20launching%20the%20ambitious%20and%20%E2%80%9CAtmanirbhar%E2%80%9D%20semiconductor%20chips%20project%20in%20Gujarat%20for%20which%20the%20Centre%20announces%20a%20grant%20of%20over%20%245%20billion.%20Modi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-inaugurate-semicon-india-2023-in-gandhinagar-today-123072800119_1.html%5C%22%3Einaugurated%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20just%20before%20the%20Gujarat%20state%20elections.%20How%20can%20a%20company%20under%20serious%20investigation%20for%20money%20laundering%20be%20part%20of%20such%20a%20prestigious%20project%20in%20which%20the%20government%20is%20pumping%20in%20Rs%2050%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20Vedanta%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ffoxconn-scraps-19-5-billion-joint-venture-with-vedanta-to-impact-indias-semiconductor-ambitions%5C%22%3Ecould%20not%20deliver%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20its%20weak%20partner%20Foxconn%20and%20eventually%20got%20out%20of%20the%20project%2C%20which%20is%20now%20being%20implemented%20by%20Tatas.%20Modi%20inaugurated%20it%20a%20week%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slow%20unravelling%20of%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scam%20will%20surely%20become%20an%20important%20conversation%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20dirty%20tricks%20department%20of%20the%20government%20will%20attempt%20multiple%20distractions%20to%20shift%20focus%20on%20other%20things.%20But%20this%20time%20it%20may%20not%20be%20so%20easy%20for%20Modi%20to%20divert%20attention.%20His%20anti-corruption%20plank%20is%20now%20full%