he%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2FMar%2F15%2Fgujarat-mlas-candid-confession-in-our-bjp-system-they-take-2-commission%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20public%20forum%20related%20to%20discussion%20on%20a%20lake%20beautification%20project%20in%20the%20Vijalpore%20area%20of%20Navsari%20district%20on%20Tuesday%20(March%2012)%2C%20the%20BJP%20MLA%20confirmed%20the%20existence%20of%20corruption%20in%20the%20saffron%20party.%20He%20instructed%20government%20job%20contractors%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20give%20money%20to%20anyone%20except%20the%202%25%20required%20within%20the%20BJP%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20Patel%20told%20contractors%20that%20Rs%204%20crore%20sanctioned%20for%20the%20lake%20beautification%20project%20should%20not%20be%20distributed%20among%20individuals%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9Cany%20contributions%20beyond%20the%20stipulated%202%25%20were%20unacceptable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20statement%2C%20the%20Congress%20underlined%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20openly%20engaging%20in%20corruption.%20Further%2C%20they%20asserted%20that%20previously%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20corrupt%20practices%20were%20%E2%80%9Cconcealed%E2%80%9D%20but%20they%20are%20now%20%E2%80%9Copenly%20acknowledged%E2%80%9D%20by%20its%20leaders%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%20%3C%2Fem%3Equoted%20Gujarat%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Hiren%20Banker%20speaking%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFormer%20BJP%20chief%20minister%20Anandi%20Ben%20Patel%20once%20stated%20that%20BJP%20workers%20have%20become%20contractors%2C%20indicating%20that%20they%20are%20more%20interested%20in%20commissions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20as%20per%20the%20country-wise%20corruption%20perception%20index%20(CPI)%20put%20together%20by%20Transparency%20International%20(