tle%22%3A%22Does%20It%20Seem%20That%20SBI%20Is%20off%20the%20Hook%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30154424%2FState_Bank_of_India_F_L_Gomes_Road_Vasco_da_Gama.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2Fp%2Felectoral-bonds-data-is-out-modi%5C%22%3Ewas%20first%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20The%20India%20Cable%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20media%20is%20celebrating%20the%20%E2%80%98slap%20on%20the%20face%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20in%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20case%20but%20when%20the%20dust%20settles%2C%20could%20the%20average%20Indian%20citizen%20be%20left%20smarting%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%20was%20to%20make%20known%20which%20purchaser%20of%20bonds%20%E2%80%98donated%E2%80%99%20how%20much%20to%20which%20party.%20The%20%E2%80%98harsh%E2%80%99%20orders%2C%20now%20given%20to%20the%20SBI%2C%20to%20quickly%20collate%20and%20reveal%20who%20purchased%20the%20bonds%20and%20who%20encashed%20them%2C%20without%20linking%20the%20buyers%20and%20the%20beneficiaries%2C%20are%20directions%20to%20provide%20data%20that%20may%20not%20serve%20the%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAnd%20the%20further%20order%20that%20the%20EC%20publish%20what%20may%20be%20more%20useful%20information%20would%20not%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20because%20the%20exercise%20of%20linking%20each%20bond%20with%20its%20purchaser%20and%20beneficiary%20can%20be%20carried%20out%20only%20by%20the%20SBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20more%20important%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20that%20linking%20the%20buyer%20with%20the%20beneficiary%20would%20not%20take%20three%20months%2C%20as%20claimed%20by%20the%20SBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20reason%20is%20that%20any%20money%20value%20security%20that%20a%20bank%20issues%20has%20an%20identifier%2C%20to%20enable%20accounting%20and%20audit%20and%20prevent%20fraud.%20If%20this%20had%20not%20been%20there%2C%20the%20value%20of%20bonds%20encashed%20could%20have%20been%20many%20times%20the%20value%20of%20the%20bonds%20purchased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20outline%20procedure%20is%20that%20on%20issue%20of%20a%20bond%2C%20or%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20issuing%20branch%20has%20to%20send%20a%20list%20of%20the%20bond%E2%80%99s%20serial%20numbers%2C%20with%20value%20to%20the%20other%20branches.%20The%20name%20of%20the%20issuer%2C%20of%20course%2C%20not%20being%20mentioned%20to%20preserve%20anonymity.%20The%20serial%20number%20being%20visible%20only%20under%20UV%20light%20is%20merely%20a%20cosmetic%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThis%20procedure%20would%20have%20been%20necessary%20so%20as%20to%20enable%20the%20encashing%20branch%2C%20when%20the%20bond%20is%20presented%2C%20to%20verify%20that%20the%20value%20has%20not%20been%20tampered%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20serial%20number%20of%20the%20bond%20issued%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20noted%20with%20the%20KYC%20documents%20of%20the%20purchaser%20of%20the%20bond.%20This%20is%20both%20for%20audit%20and%20to%20satisfy%20a%20claim%20by%20a%20purchaser%2C%20if%20made%2C%20that%20a%20bond%20was%20paid%20for%20a%20different%20value%20or%20misappropriated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EWith%20this%20data%20in%20place%2C%20as%20it%20must%20be%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20major%20task%20to%20connect%20the%20purchaser%20and%20the%20beneficiary%20of%20each%20bond%2C%20upon%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20court%2C%20as%20is%20provided%20for%20in%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ETo%20illustrate%3A%20There%20are%20approximately%2022%2C000%20bonds.%20Entering%20the%20data%20of%20purchaser%2C%20value%20and%20serial%20number%20of%20each%20bond%2C%20available%20in%20the%20respective%20sealed%20envelope%2C%20into%20a%20spreadsheet%2C%20cannot%20take%20more%20than%20a%20minute%2C%20with%20two%20persons%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E22%2C000%20bonds%20would%20hence%20take%2022%2C000%2F60%3D%20366%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20second%20task%2C%20of%20entering%20the%20data%20of%20who%20encashed%20each%20bond%20would%20take%20less%20time%2C%20as%20there%20are%20very%20few%20beneficiary%20parties%2C%20and%20only%20a%20code%20to%20identify%20the%20party%20need%20be%20entered%2C%20or%20the%20bonds%20could%20be%20sorted%20party-wise%20before%20data%20entry.%20Say%20this%20takes%20234%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20total%20time%20is%20366%2B234%20%3D%20600%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EIf%2020%20teams%20of%20two%20persons%20are%20deployed%2C%20the%20job%20will%20be%20over%20in%2010%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EGetting%20the%20information%20of%20how%20much%20each%20donor%20gave%20each%20party%20will%20now%20take%20a%20few%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20a%20conclusion%20that%20any%20(competent)%20bank%20employee%2C%20who%20has%20dealt%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20demand%20drafts%2C%20public%20issues%2C%20etc.%20and%20then%20with%20reconciliation%20of%20accounts%2C%20would%20have%20arrived%20at%20instantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20bank%E2%80%99s%20advocate%20tried%20to%20say%20that%20linking%20the%20donor%20with%20beneficiary%20is%20what%20was%20required%20to%20be%20done.%20Instead%2C%20the%20court%20read%20their%20order%20of%20February%2015%20as%20only%20listing%20out%20the%20donors%20and%20the%20receivers%2C%20without%20the%20connections%20and%20ordered%20that%20this%20be%20done%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EInstead%2C%20the%20court%20should%20have%20questioned%20the%20bank%20on%20why%20the%20exercise%20needs%20three%20months%2C%20and%20the%20order%20could%20have%20been%20to%20put%20out%20the%20real%20information%20in%2048%20hours%2C%20if%20not%20in%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EDoes%20it%20seem%20that%20SBI%20is%20off%20the%20hook%3F%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EA%20further%20order%20from%20the%20court%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20possible%2C%20on%20application%2C%20if%20not%20%3Cem%3Esuo%20motto%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20author%20is%20a%20retired%20civil%20servant%20who%20also%20spent%20some%20years%20as%20an%20SBI%20officer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710491435000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30154424%2FState_Bank_of_India_F_L_Gomes_Road_Vasco_da_Gama.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fdoes-it-seem-that-sbi-is-off-the-hook%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Linking%20the%20buyer%20with%20the%20beneficiary%20would%20not%20take%20three%20months%2C%20as%20claimed%20by%20the%20SBI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fdoes-it-seem-that-sbi-is-off-the-hook%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Judge%20rejects%20Trump's%20bid%20to%20throw%20out%20classified%20documents%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710488580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-donald-trump-business_6456592.jpg%3F20240315081941%22%2C%