oss%20the%2030%20centres%2C%20with%2028%20of%20them%20operating%20in%20partnership%20with%20different%20State%20Governments%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Meghalaya%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20remaining%20two%20are%20privately%20managed%20by%20the%20foundation.%20The%20private%20centres%2C%20present%20in%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Punjab%2C%20offer%20dialysis%20at%20subsidised%20rates.%20The%20foundation%20is%20also%20soon%20planning%20to%20expand%20to%20even%20more%20centres%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20State%20Governments%20of%20Jharkhand%20and%20Punjab%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chandrakala%2C%20an%20ASHA%20worker%2C%20who%20availed%20the%20benefit%20of%20The%20Hans%20Renal%20Centre%20in%20Karnaprayag.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344876%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChandrakala%2C%20an%20ASHA%20worker%2C%20who%20availed%20the%20benefit%20of%20The%20Hans%20Renal%20Centre%20in%20Karnaprayag.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20patients%2