20on%20the%20sustainability%20route.%20All%20their%20wooden%20products%20are%20made%20from%20fallen%3Cem%3E%20chikoo%3C%2Fem%3E%20twigs%20and%20branches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESustainability%20is%20also%20a%20winner%20in%20Brijesh%E2%80%99s%20neighbouring%20handloom%20stall%20belonging%20to%20the%20Bodo%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331624%2Fassam-man-quits-his-job-to-make-sustainable-toys-that-represent-assams-tribes-and-culture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribes%20of%20Assam%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20our%20cotton%20clothes%20are%20made%20from%20natural%20colours%20that%20last%20forever%20and%20are%20also%20good%20for%20the%20skin.%20We%20make%20colours%20from%20turmeric%2C%20leaves%20from%20plants%20and%20a%20few%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaison%20Bhramo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyotisankar%20Sahu%20of%20the%20Sabar%20tribe%20from%20Odisha%20is%20here%20for%20the%20second%20time.%20For%20him%2C%20the%20best%20benefit%20of%20putting%20up%20a%20stall%20is%20making%20his%20digital%20debut.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20a%20group%20of%2070%20people%20who%20make%20brass%20showpieces.%20We%20always%20get%20orders%20after%20we%20return%20home%20from%20the%20conclave.%20Samvaad%20is%20a%20good%20platform%20to%20preserve%20our%20culture%20and%20tell%20the%20world%20about%20the%20exceptional%20skills%20that%20we%20learnt%20from%20our%20ancestors%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20exposure%2C%20the%20artisans%20are%20also%20happy%20to%20see%20people%20taking%20an%20interest%20in%20their%20traditions.%20Sangeeta%20Meda%20from%20the%20Bhil%20tribe%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20second%20time%20here%2C%20and%20people%20always%20ask%20us%20about%20our%20history%20and%20the%20significance%20of%20our%20Bhil%20Pithora%20paintings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20ancestors%20would%20make%20these%20dotted%20paintings%20on%20walls%20during%20festivities.%20Gradually%2C%20they%20moved%20onto%20paper.%20Our%20paintings%20tell%20the%20stories%20of%20our%20origin%20and%20who%20we%20are.%20While%20selling%2C%20we%20let%20the%20customers%20know%20our%20intention%20behind%20choosing%20a%20particular%20colour%20and%20theme.%20They%20feel%20connected%20to%20us.%20My%20grandmother%2C%20Buri%20Bai%2C%20was%20awarded%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20her%20preservation%20efforts.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20carry%20forward%20her%20legacy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangeeta%20shares%20that%20the%20family%20starts%20the%20work%20nearly%20eight%20months%20before%20Samvaad%20as%20it%20takes%2010%20days%20to%20make%20one%20painting.%20She%20happily%20adds%20that%20their%20paintings%20sell%20like%20hotcakes!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20stall%20displaying%20products%20featuring%20Warli%20art.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-2048x1152.jpg%