ing%20opportunity%20was%20missing.%20We%20attended%20a%20workshop%20at%20Samvaad%20and%20learned%20that%20new%20designs%20can%20be%20implemented%20on%20pillow%20covers%2C%20cushion%20covers%2C%20T-shirts%2C%20etc.%20In%20our%20second%20year%2C%20we%20did%20that%20and%20made%20profits.%20I%20also%20made%20friends%20from%20other%20tribal%20communities%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20fashion%20trends%20across%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Yazile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20art%20and%20craft%20workshops%20helped%20artists%20like%20Yazile%20and%20Dinabandhu%20post-pandemic%20when%20the%20market%20crashed%20and%20selling%20at%20local%20%3Cem%3Ehaats%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecame%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20building%20online%20market%20links%20for%2026%20tribal%20communities%20representing%2030%20art%20forms.%20We%20wanted%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3EToda%3C%2Fem%3E%20embroidery%20of%20Nilgiris%2C%20%3Cem%3EMuga%20%3C%2Fem%3Esilk%20of%20Assam%2C%20and%20more%20as%20popular%20as%20%3Cem%3EBanarasi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EIkat%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EChikankari%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20brought%20in%20experts%20from%20NIFT%20and%20NID%20to%20impart%20the%20skills%2C%20colour%20combinations%2C%20motifs%2C%20etc%2C%20that%20meet%20customer%20demands%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Smita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CTrends%20in%20the%20metro%20change%20fast%2C%20so%20we%20ask%20them%20not%20to%20change%20their%20cultural%20identity.%C2%A0%20But%20they%20can%20experiment%20with%20colours%20and%20motifs.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20pastel%20colour%20is%20in%20the%20market%2C%20infuse%20those%20colours%20in%20the%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thronging%20crowds%20at%20handicraft%20stalls%20were%20proof%20that%20the%20workshops%20were%20beneficial.%20Chaaya%20Saraiwala%2C%20an%20attendee%2C%20purchased%20Yazile%E2%80%99s%20shawls%20and%20Brijesh%E2%80%99s%20fridge%20magnets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20first%20time%20atte